nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE CONTINUES WEST-NORTHWESTWARD FAR TO THE EAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE CONTINUES WEST-NORTHWESTWARD FAR TO THE EAST OF HAWAII... As of 5:00 PM HST Tue Aug 05 the center of Henriette was located near 17.6, -126.9 with movement WNW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
